=====================================================================
PAXLE - IP-LOCATOR BUNDLE
=====================================================================

Description:
--------------------------------------------------------------------- 
This bundle can be used to determine the locale for a given
host-name of ip-address and returns the flag of the detected
country. The available flags are located in /resources/flags/.

This bundle registers a servlet that is available via 
   http://[server]:[port]/ipLocator
an accepts an URL as request parameter, e.g.
   http://[server]:[port]/ipLocator?ip=paxel.sourceforge.net

Sourcecode:
---------------------------------------------------------------------
SVN:  svn+ssh://svn@svn.xenim.de/p2psearch/trunk/bundles/IPLocatorTools
HTTP: http://trac.paxle.net/trac/browser/trunk/bundles/IPLocatorTools

Dynamic Imports:
--------------------------------------------------------------------- 
- sun.reflect

Used External Bundles:
--------------------------------------------------------------------- 
- Knopflerfish Framework 
- Knopflerfish Servlet.jar (jsdk)
  
Used Paxle Bundles:
--------------------------------------------------   
- Paxle Core
  
Used External Libraries:
--------------------------------------------------
- InetAddressLocator: Java IP geolocation system
  Files: InetAddressLocator.jar
  See: http://javainetlocator.sourceforge.net
- Flag-Icons
  Files: /resources/flags/*
  See: http://famfamfam.com/lab/icons/flags/    
  